OL,3,CSEN children 'face cliff edge when
OL,4,Cschool ends'
OL,6,FA parent of a teenager with special
OL,7,Feducational needs says children like
OL,8,Fher son are facing a cliff edge once
OL,9,Ftheir time in school comes to an end.
OL,11,FCurrently, when pupils with moderate
OL,12,Flearning difficulties leave school
OL,13,Faged 19, many are left without
OL,14,Fprovisions in place - something which
OL,15,Fdiffers from other parts of the UK.
OL,17,FWith just a few years left of
OL,18,Fteaching, Alma White says she feels
OL,19,Fforced to put up a fight for her son
OL,20,FCaleb.
