OL,6,F"His mental age is not going to be 19,
OL,7,Fhe's got maybe the mental age of an
OL,8,Feight or nine-year-old and he's very
OL,9,Fvulnerable," she told UTV.
OL,11,F"And also his disabilities and his
OL,12,Fneeds don't change at 19, they don't
OL,13,Fdisappear."
OL,15,FIn other parts of the UK, special
OL,16,Fneeds pupils are given provisions up
OL,17,Fto the age of 25 from when they leave
OL,18,Fschool.
