OL,6,FThat includes things like accessing
OL,7,Ffurther education. But in Northern
OL,8,FIreland, there are no plans in place,
OL,9,Fleaving teachers and parents in limbo.
OL,11,FAlma's calls for change are echoed by
OL,12,Fthose tasked with supporting young
OL,13,Fpeople.
OL,15,FChris Quinn, Commissioner for Children
OL,16,Fand Young People, said: "I would urge
OL,17,Feach of the ministers in government to
OL,18,Fwork alongside the education minister
OL,19,Fto prioritise children in the
OL,20,Fprogramme for government."
